### Get all progress history entries
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get progress history with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history?volunteerId=USER_ID&status=completed&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get my progress history
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/my-history?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get my trends
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/my-trends
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get volunteer trends (Admin only or own data)
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/volunteer/VOLUNTEER_ID/trends
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get analytics summary (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/analytics/summary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get monthly summary for all volunteers (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/monthly/2024/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get monthly summary for specific volunteer
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/monthly/2024/1?volunteerId=USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get volunteer monthly summary
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/volunteer/VOLUNTEER_ID/monthly/2024/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get specific progress history entry
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/PROGRESS_HISTORY_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Create progress history entry (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/progress-history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Advanced NestJS",
  "goalId": "GOAL_ID",
  "volunteerId": "VOLUNTEER_ID",
  "progress": 85,
  "notes": "Completed modules on authentication and database integration",
  "weekStart": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "weekEnd": "2024-01-07T23:59:59.999Z",
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Delete progress history entry (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/progress-history/PROGRESS_HISTORY_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN


### Get volunteer's weekly history
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/volunteer/VOLUNTEER_ID/weekly-history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get volunteer's weekly history with date range
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/volunteer/VOLUNTEER_ID/weekly-history?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-03-31
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get my weekly history (what your frontend will call)
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/my-weekly-history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get my weekly history with date range
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/my-weekly-history?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-03-31
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get volunteer's most productive day in current week
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/volunteer/VOLUNTEER_ID/productive-day
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get my most productive day in current week
GET http://localhost:3000/progress-history/my-productive-day
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN